	<tag>
		<description>
			<![CDATA[
    
 TabPane is a special implementation of TabControl. It includes all TabControl functions and features,
 but extends them to include an HTML panel grid to create a complete tab pane.
 You can add practically any number of standard JSF components you need to create a complete pane.
    
  ]]>
		</description>
		<name>tabpane</name>
		<tag-class>ecruiser.advanced.tab.tag.TabPaneTag</tag-class>
