	</tag>

	<tag>
		<description>
			<![CDATA[
    
      The main ECruiser component class for displaying hierarchical data as a Tree. A tree contains one or more
      {@link TreeCell}s, which are JSF components that render the individual tree nodes. In most cases, tree cells
      are re-used in rendering the data provided by the model -- in much the same way as rows are re-used in rendering
      {@link javax.faces.component.UIData} or {@link ecruiser.advanced.datatable.DataTable}.
        
  ]]>
		</description>
		<name>tree</name>
		<tag-class>ecruiser.advanced.tree.tag.TreeTag</tag-class>
		<body-content>JSP</body-content>
