	<tag>
		<description>
			<![CDATA[
    
    A TreeCell represents the visible nodes of a {@link Tree}. TreeCells can be either static nodes or template
      cells that are re-rendered for nodes provided by the {@link ecruiser.advanced.tree.model.TreeModel}.
    
  ]]>
		</description>
